download_font           Download font files
generate_css            Generate CSS to import fonts
get_all_fonts           Get infos about all fonts available
get_font_info           Get detailed information about a font
gfonts                  Use Google fonts offline
included_fonts          Detail about included fonts.
setup_font              Setup a font to be used in Shiny or Markdown
tag_example             Generate HTML tags used in examples
use_font                Use a downloaded font in Shiny or Markdown
use_pkg_gfont           Use a Google Font included in gfonts
